message: Hello Bob! I'm excited to offer you this incredible product. I think it's a game-changer and I'm confident you'll love it. I'm willing to sell it to you for $1,400,000. This is a great deal, considering the product's value to you is $1,500,000. I'm willing to make a concession to get it to you, but I'm still confident you'll see the value in it. What do you think?
